  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nIf you leave off the semicolon on an import statement, a pegjs error will be shown with the line number but not the filename in which the problem is occurring. This adds unnecessary troubleshooting steps for a trivial syntax error if there are many contracts in the project.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nRemove the semicolon from the end of the import statement in `MetaCoin.sol` and attempt to compile:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nimport \"./ConvertLib.sol\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nShould give a syntax error like browser-solidity:\r\n\r\n```\r\nMetaCoin.sol:5:1: Error: Expected token Semicolon got 'Contract'\r\ncontract MetaCoin {\r\n^\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nCompilation fails with no indication of which file the error is in:\r\n\r\n```sh\r\n/Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/solidity-parser/index.js:39\r\n      throw e;\r\n      ^\r\nSyntaxError: Expected \"/*\", \"//\", \";\", \"as\", comment, end of line or whitespace but \"c\" found. Line: 10, Column: 1\r\n    at peg$buildException (/Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/solidity-parser/build/imports_parser.js:487:14)\r\n    at Object.peg$parse [as parse] (/Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/solidity-parser/build/imports_parser.js:4080:13)\r\n    at Object.module.exports.parse (/Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/solidity-parser/index.js:34:23)\r\n    at /Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/truffle/lib/profiler.js:242:38\r\n    at /Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/truffle/lib/sources.js:37:7\r\n    at /Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/async/lib/async.js:789:30\r\n    at /Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/async/lib/async.js:167:37\r\n    at /Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/truffle/lib/sources.js:22:9\r\n    at /Users/raine/test/truffle-test/node_modules/truffle/lib/sources/fs.js:15:12\r\n    at tryToString (fs.js:449:3)\r\n    at FSReqWrap.readFileAfterClose [as oncomplete] (fs.js:436:12)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: OSX El Capitan\r\n* Truffle version: 3.0.0-4\r\n* Ethereum client: N/A\r\n* node version: 6.1.0\r\n* npm version: 3.8.6\r\n",
